OL,3,CTeacher stabbed woman 15 times after
OL,4,Crelationship ended - court told
OL,6,FA teacher has told a jury how she was
OL,7,Fattacked by her on-off boyfriend after
OL,8,Fhe would not accept their relationship
OL,9,Fwas over.
OL,11,FMatthew Jones, 28, stabbed Emma Kirk,
OL,12,F24, around 15 times with a knife,
OL,13,Finflicting multiple injuries to her
OL,14,Fneck, head and face.
OL,16,FBristol Crown Court heard the "angry"
OL,17,Fdefendant, also a teacher, allegedly
OL,18,Fattacked Miss Kirk because he would
OL,19,Fnot accept she did not want to see him
OL,20,Fagain.
