OL,3,CTeacher stabbed woman 15 times after
OL,4,Crelationship ended - court told
OL,6,FThe jury was told it took five men to
OL,7,Fdrag him off Miss Kirk and even then
OL,8,Fhe tried to strangle her during the
OL,9,Fattack in Bath in February.
OL,11,FMiss Kirk, a secondary school teacher,
OL,12,Ftold the jury they had become friends
OL,13,Fwhile completing their training at
OL,14,Funiversity in 2022.
OL,16,FShe said over the next 18 months they
OL,17,Fbecame "very close" and were intimate
OL,18,Fon a couple of occasions.
