OL,3,CTeacher stabbed woman 15 times after
OL,4,Crelationship ended - court told
OL,6,F"By the end of November or early
OL,7,FDecember I decided I wanted to put
OL,8,Fsome boundaries up in our
OL,9,Frelationship," she said.
OL,11,FLooking at dozens of WhatsApp messages
OL,12,Fof their conversations, Miss Kirk
OL,13,Fbroke down in tears, telling the jury:
OL,14,F"I know that we were close. It's very
OL,15,Fhard to look at all those messages...
OL,16,FI know we were close.
OL,18,F"It's upsetting because I made it
OL,19,Fclear that I thought we were friends.
OL,20,FIt's very hard having to look at these
OL,21,Fafter what happened to me."
