OL,3,CTeacher stabbed woman 15 times after
OL,4,Crelationship ended - court told
OL,6,FThe court heard Miss Kirk and Jones
OL,7,Fagreed to meet in a lane near her home
OL,8,Fbecause he wanted back gifts he had
OL,9,Fbought her.
OL,11,FMichael Haynes, representing Jones,
OL,12,Fsuggested to Miss Kirk she was scared
OL,13,Fof the defendant and had put on
OL,14,Ftrainers and taken a knife with her in
OL,15,Fcase she needed to flee.
OL,17,FMiss Kirk replied: "That's incorrect."
