OL,6,F"What I am going to suggest is what
OL,7,Fhappened at the incident is that when
OL,8,Fyou met Matthew you threw the bags
OL,9,Fdown on the floor and you were
OL,10,Fterrified and scared of him and you
OL,11,Fwere going to get him arrested and
OL,12,Fthat's when you ran off," Mr Haynes
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FShe replied: "No, that's not what
OL,16,Fhappened."
OL,18,FFighting back tears, she added: "He
OL,19,Fsaid he wanted to be with me and I
OL,20,Fdidn't feel the same way.
