OL,6,FAn off-duty police officer, members of
OL,7,Fthe public and paramedics went to
OL,8,Fassist her in the lane close to
OL,9,FDransfield Way and administered first
OL,10,Faid.
OL,12,FThe defendant, of Ivy Avenue,
OL,13,FSouthdown, Bath, denies attempted
OL,14,Fmurder and having an article with a
OL,15,Fblade or point in a public place, but
OL,16,Fhe admits causing grievous bodily harm
OL,17,Fwith intent.
OL,19,FThe trial continues.
